# HKMetadataKeyAlgorithmVersion

**Global Variable**

A key that indicates the version number of the algorithm used to calculate the sample’s value.

## Declaration

```swift
let HKMetadataKeyAlgorithmVersion: String
```

## Discussion

This key takes an [doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/Foundation/NSNumber] containing an [doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/ObjectiveC/NSInteger].
